author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the deterioration of the Internet. It seems every service both big and small are filling the Internet with so much junk it's become a chore to explore it like I once enjoyed. In all this thankfully the first layer of the Internet still exists and their are ways to explore what once made the net so great. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Internet Kinda Sucks Now...
